# Contract-First Prompting (2026)

This is a modernized text version of the legacy prompt.

## Purpose
Convert ambiguous user intent into a testable execution contract before implementation.

## Required Sections
- Objective
- Scope/In-scope vs Out-of-scope
- Inputs and assumptions
- Acceptance criteria (observable)
- Risks and fallback plan
- Approval gate before execution

## Interaction Rules
- Ask targeted questions in priority order.
- Summarize decisions after each major clarification.
- Do not proceed to implementation without explicit approval.
